  "description_snippet": "On Chrome on Android after patch crrev.com/c/3990410 the fullscreen notification toast is now displayed in bottom instead of top position, if shown in the bottom position I found that Android keyboard able to overlap fullscreen notification toast, so user will not see the fullscreen toast.  \n  \n**VE"
